column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.extinction_i,   s.specobjid , s.z AS zs, s.class, s.subclass, s.zErr, s.elodieSpType, s.elodieObject,   w.w1mag AS w1, w.w2mag AS w2 from WISE_xmatch AS xm   JOIN photoObjAll AS p ON xm.sdss_objid = p.objid   JOIN WISE_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr   LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
